smfStateObjectsGroup OBJECT-GROUP OBJECTS { smfNodeRsStatusIncluded, smfNeighborRSSA, smfNeighborNextHopInterface } STATUS current DESCRIPTION "Set of SMF state objects implemented in this module." ::= { smfMIBGroups 2 }
smfPerfObjectsGroup OBJECT-GROUP OBJECTS { smfMultiPktsRecvTotal, smfMultiPktsForwardedTotal, smfDuplMultiPktsDetectedTotal, smfDroppedMultiPktsTTLExceededTotal, smfMultiPktsRecvPerIf, smfMultiPktsForwardedPerIf, smfDuplMultiPktsDetectedPerIf, smfDroppedMultiPktsTTLExceededPerIf } STATUS current DESCRIPTION "Set of SMF performance objects implemented in this module by total and per interface." ::= { smfMIBGroups 3 }
